customset

Class CustomSet<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • customset.CustomSet<T>

  • public class CustomSet<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object

    The implementation of my custom set

    The CustomSet class is a generic class that uses the notion of binary search tree to easily implement the main functionality of the Java TreeSet.

    Info: The main methods of the program are 'add()', 'remove()', 'contains()' and 'getSize()'.
